<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Professional Programmer Survey</h1>
      <p>A survey to understand the habits and preferences of professional programmers</p>
    </header>
    
    <main>
      <section class="intro">
        <h2>Welcome to our Survey</h2>
        <p>
          Programming is an essential skill for engineers of all fields as it enables effective communication with digital machines.
          This survey aims to collect data about professional programmers to better understand their backgrounds, tools, and habits.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your participation will help us gather valuable insights about the programming community.
        </p>
        
        <div class="actions">
          <a href="/survey" class="btn primary">Take the Survey</a>
          <a href="/submissions" class="btn secondary">View Submissions</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Professional Programmer Survey</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
